    dc:description "Figure 3. Amara (Curtonotus) gansuensis A dorsal habitus, male (Mentougou District, Beijing) B pronotum posterior angle C male mesotibia D lateral view of aedeagus E right paramere F apical lamella G female gonocoxite (Chongli, Hebei). Scale bars: 5 mm (A); 1 mm (B-E); 0.5 mm (F, G)." ;
